    public class VirtualMachineExtended
extends fr.upmc.datacenter.software.applicationvm.ApplicationVM
implements VMExtendedManagementI
    The class VirtualMachineExtended implements a component that represents an Virtual Machine in a datacenter.

    Description

    It Extend the Actual Virtual Machine to offer more Services like adding cores or removing cores directly by the VM.
    Author:
    Cédric Ribeiro et Mokrane Kadri
